{"tid":2079614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邵嵐：【拆解美國《香港自治法》｜究竟有幾辣？】","createTime":"2020-06-26T02:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T11:24:57.000Z","uid":70063,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"feabd9003e38c5a1f5d7f2089233fae4d6b7864b","tid":2079614,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:01:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺美國參議院通過嘅《香港自治法》之所以咁「辣」，係因為幾個因素：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>#九十日內落實制裁</strong>🧑🏻&zwj;⚖️<br />\n美國政府須於法案生效後90日內選擇最少一名須為中共違反《#中英聯合聲明》負責嘅人士作為制裁目標。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>#全面禁止金融交易</strong>💸<br />\n制裁目標嘅 #銀行交易將被拒絕，同時亦不可進行任何支付款項嘅行動，另外其外匯交易亦會被停止。換句說話嚟講，姐係 #喺金融層面全面封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>#制裁法案打到嚟港九新界都無得避～</strong><br />\n「我唔喺美國境內做交易咪無事囉～」唔係！講到明禁止外匯交易，姐係你喺美國境外亦都會被制裁到啊～🥳<br />\n<br />\n另外我之前發起嘅聯署仲開放緊架！一齊簽名集氣推到眾議院加速審議程序！🙌🏻<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《支持香港自治法｜Support Hong Kong Autonomy Act》</strong>🖋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/SupportHongKongAutonomtAct\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2FSupportHongKongAutonomtAct&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=74e46312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/SupportHongKongAutonomtAct</a><br />\n<br />\n#StandWithHK<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\nTwitter @jooeysiiu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108032190900473/posts/138954794474879/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108032190900473%2Fposts%2F138954794474879%2F&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=ac262c7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108032190900473/posts/138954794474879/</a>"},{"pid":"215d558cec2c3e0ba75f9138346b785600cab877","tid":2079614,"uid":129348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMJwxgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMJwxgX.jpg&h=db86ecf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br /